                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18101031-68-off423 t18101031-68-cd424"></join>, sixteen yards of woolen cloth, value 16 l. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18101031-68-victim796" type="victimName">
