                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18101031-68-defend792 t18101031-68-deflabel428"></join> of mine: I had her sister to be a servant with me before, they both conducted themselves as honest persons.</p>
               <p>
                  <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="181010310059"></xptr>Q. Did you know that the piece of cloth was in your house - A. Yes; I called the young woman to give me information how it came there. I sent for Stanton.</p>
